  "title": "Aurelius, Meditations §aur_07_xi: Of things that are external, happen what will to that which can suffer by ext...",
  "body": "Of things that are external, happen what will to that which can suffer by external accidents. Those things that suffer let them complain themselves, if they will; as for me, as long as I conceive no such thing, that that which is happened is evil, I have no hurt; and it is in my power not to conceive any such thing.",
